column1: Bee data from Threlfall et al Journal of Applied Ecology 'Increasing biodiversity in urban green spaces through simple vegetation interventions'
For data collection methods see above paper.

spp = species. Point = green space site (n=39). Rep = plot within each green space. Season = spring and summer sampling seasons as  detailed in the paper. Homalictus (Homalictus) complex: punctatus, brisbanensis and megastigmus
